df %>% distinct(link, .keep_all = TRUE) %>% ggplot(aes(x = wday))+geom_bar()+facet_wrap(~site) -> g
print(g)

#    
df %>% filter(outlier==TRUE) %>% distinct(link, .keep_all = TRUE) %>% ggplot(aes(x = wday))+geom_bar()+facet_wrap(~site)-> g
print(g)

#  
df %>% distinct(link, .keep_all = TRUE) %>% ggplot(aes(x = month))+geom_bar()+facet_wrap(~site)-> g
print(g)

df %>% filter(outlier==TRUE) %>% distinct(link, .keep_all = TRUE) %>% ggplot(aes(x = month))+geom_bar()+facet_wrap(~site)-> g
print(g)

df %>% distinct(link, .keep_all = TRUE) %>% ggplot(aes(x = wday, fill=site))+geom_bar()-> g
print(g)

#    
df %>% filter(outlier==TRUE) %>% distinct(link, .keep_all = TRUE) %>% ggplot(aes(x = wday, fill=site))+geom_bar()-> g
print(g)

df %>% distinct(link, .keep_all = TRUE) %>% ggplot(aes(x = month, fill=site))+geom_bar()-> g
print(g)

#    
df %>% filter(outlier==TRUE) %>% distinct(link, .keep_all = TRUE) %>% ggplot(aes(x = month, fill=site))+geom_bar()-> g
print(g)

df %>% distinct(link, .keep_all = TRUE) %>% group_by(wday, site) %>% summarise(n=n()) %>% mutate(prop=n/sum(n)) %>% ungroup() %>% ggplot(aes(x = wday, y = prop, fill = site)) + 
  geom_bar(position = "fill",stat = "identity")+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format())-> g
print(g)

df %>% distinct(link, .keep_all = TRUE) %>% group_by(month, site) %>% summarise(n=n()) %>% mutate(prop=n/sum(n)) %>% ungroup() %>% ggplot(aes(x = month, y = prop, fill = site)) + 
  geom_bar(position = "fill",stat = "identity")+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format())-> g
print(g)

#   (  )
df %>% group_by(wday, site) %>%  ggplot(aes(x = wday, fill = site))+geom_bar()+facet_wrap(~item, ncol = 3)

df %>% group_by(month, site) %>%  ggplot(aes(x = month, fill = site))+geom_bar()+facet_wrap(~item, ncol = 3)-> g
print(g)

# wday.     (   ) 
df %>% filter(outlier==TRUE) %>% group_by(wday, site, item) %>%
  summarise(n=n()) %>% mutate(prop=n/sum(n)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = wday, y = prop, fill = site))+
  geom_bar(position = "fill",stat = "identity")+facet_wrap(~item, ncol = 3)+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format())-> g
print(g)

# month.     (   ) 
df %>% filter(outlier==TRUE) %>% group_by(month, site, item) %>%
  summarise(n=n()) %>% mutate(prop=n/sum(n)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = month, y = prop, fill = site))+
  geom_bar(position = "fill",stat = "identity")+facet_wrap(~item, ncol = 3)+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format())-> g
print(g)

# wday.  ""    (   ) 
df %>% filter(outlier==TRUE) %>%  group_by(wday, site, item) %>%
  mutate(prop=similarity/sum(similarity)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = wday, y = prop, fill = site))+
  geom_bar(position = "fill",stat = "identity")+facet_wrap(~item, ncol = 3)+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format())-> g
print(g)

# month.  ""    (   )
df %>% filter(outlier==TRUE) %>% group_by(month, site, item) %>%
  mutate(prop=similarity/sum(similarity)) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = month, y = prop, fill = site))+
  geom_bar(position = "fill",stat = "identity")+facet_wrap(~item, ncol = 3)+
  scale_y_continuous(labels = scales::percent_format())-> g
print(g)
